paths: Obvious exits: north, northeast, west, northwest, out
description: Golden orbs hang from the ceiling, providing ample lighting for the foyer that is surrounded by white stucco walls.  Teak floorboards stretch to the north, northeast, and northwest, their smooth surfaces glistening beneath a polished patina.  Tacked to one wall is a painted sign.
title: [Cobbling Warehouse, Foyer]
